{"tid":1246366,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇下主張脫支嘅美國華人點睇香港","createTime":"2019-06-20T16:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T10:40:49.000Z","uid":69221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9693f10d57c728e5433e5cbe1f4c1f2e15eb82b4","tid":1246366,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZPXHx_EBX8U&amp;ab_channel=%E8%A3%A4%E8%AE%BA-%E5%BE%90%E6%80%9D%E8%BF%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZPXHx_EBX8U%26ab_channel%3D%25E8%25A3%25A4%25E8%25AE%25BA-%25E5%25BE%2590%25E6%2580%259D%25E8%25BF%259C&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rantWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=48386fc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZPXHx_EBX8U&amp;ab_channel=%E8%A3%A4%E8%AE%BA-%E5%BE%90%E6%80%9D%E8%BF%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去New York 反送中集會<br />\n<br />\n冇字幕同埋重口音<br />\n我打左一部分岀黎<br />\n<br />\n「香港人自97年遊行示威越來越頻繁<br />\n除了因為共產黨嘅邪惡還有來自香港人本身的原因<br />\n<br />\n香港人接受了一百年英國統治，語言習慣、道德習俗到法律傳統上和大陸人已經不是同一個民族，所以才會不斷發動大規模遊行。<br />\n但他們學英美學得不夠，因為他們還沒做好民族和國家嘅建構。<br />\n在這種沒有大陸切割斷奶的情況下<br />\n<br />\n民族大一統，家國天下的情緒就堵絕了自由的道路。<br />\n我小時候都受過霍元甲，中國心這種作品影響，這種作品是非常邪惡的，他已經把一種國家的認同凌駕於個人自由之上<br />\n<br />\n很多人在糾結昨天晚上有多少香港人出來，我看來實際上是沒有用的。<br />\n當他的國家認同和民族認同還沒有形成時，說句難聽的話就是當他還沒有共和軍，自由軍，沒有街頭戰役的時候。所有和平理性非暴力的抗爭都會失敗。<br />\n因為他們所面對的那個集團，那個對生命沒有適當看法的種群是不一樣<br />\n<br />\n共産黨可以使用所有非人類的手段來實現所謂的大國崛起<br />\n<br />\n僅散散步和叫叫口號是遠遠不夠的」<br />\n<br />\n現場有人舉上海獨立旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yKDTqZ65tgQ&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyKDTqZ65tgQ%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rantWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=7448a200\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yKDTqZ65tgQ&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由中國人嘅觀點岀法，去講解中共嘅制度點樣令到中國人變成違背普世價值嘅垃圾群族<br />\n<br />\nhongL C<br />\n1 小時前<br />\n听你的视频觉得挺可怕的  就像以为自己只是长了个瘤子.  然后你居然跟我说已经晚期了...."},{"pid":"95b288e65e9bc0735db7f05b3d7aa40f2c055598","tid":1246366,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33b9aeffad90d683e906c5f74fd119b22bad988","tid":1246366,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6199241a61fad548db381958e7cab138b8c69480","tid":1246366,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}